1
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:37,376
(Adapted from the Jinjiang
Literature City novel, "Dazzling")

2
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,976
(Original work by Shi Jiu Yuan)

3
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,440
(Episode 15)

4
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,480
Zhu Feng.

5
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,840
Did you hear?

6
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,976
Your ex-wife and Xing Wu's mom

7
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,680
fought and ended up at the police station.

8
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,320
What? The police station?

9
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,640
How is that possible?
Don't listen to those rumors.

10
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,520
Ask around if you don't believe me.

11
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,896
Let me tell you, it wasn't easy for you

12
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,280
to get a top student like Qing Ye.

13
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,456
You mustn't let

14
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,000
your family matters affect her.

15
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:46,120
Don't let her end up like...

16
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,320
Xing Wu.

17
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,840
(Xuandao Show Hair Salon)

18
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:58,120
Why isn't this light box working?

19
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,680
It was fine yesterday.

20
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,760
When bad luck strikes,

21
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,920
everything goes wrong.

22
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,977
Just my luck!

23
00:03:04,001 --> 00:03:05,080
(Xuandao Show Hair Salon)

24
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,880
What's going on here?

25
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,960
Is there a power outage?

26
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,960
It's probably a loose connection.

27
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,720
I'll fix it in a bit.

28
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,360
How is Grandma doing?

29
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,560
I've admitted her to the hospital.

30
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,080
Shu Han is watching over her now.

31
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,256
- Don't worry.
- Fang Fang.

32
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,280
She's fine.

33
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,760
You're back.

34
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,160
What exactly happened?

35
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,776
Come on, let's talk inside Love Mahjong.

36
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,440
Let's go. We'll talk inside Love Mahjong.

37
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:33,320
- Are you okay?
- What could be wrong with me?

38
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,360
So Shu Han is taking care of Grandma?

39
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,080
Canine and Shu Han

40
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,280
will take turns tonight.

41
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,920
I'll bring a few things over tomorrow.

42
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,720
The surgery will be expensive, right?

43
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,880
Is there anything I can do to help?

44
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,200
Don't you worry about that.

45
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,400
You're a student.

46
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,600
Just focus on your studies.

47
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,800
(Xuandao Show Hair Salon)

48
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,400
(Xuandao Show Hair Salon)

49
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,920
Why are you back?

50
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,680
Grandma is more important.

51
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,136
I just came by to see

52
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,600
if there's anything I can help with.

53
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,640
It's fine. Don't worry about it.

54
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,816
Can you stop trying to carry

55
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,080
everything on your own?

56
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:56,600
I may seem heartless,

57
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,480
but that's only because

58
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,880
I'm trying to give myself a way out.

59
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,800
For Grandma's surgery,

60
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,760
we might need over 10,000 yuan.

61
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,520
I know.

62
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,760
I'll find a way.

63
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,920
I'll find a way too.

64
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,000
- Yu Fen.
- Fang Fang.

65
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,600
Why did you leave so suddenly?

66
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,400
We know you're in a tough spot.

67
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,600
Don't be shy about asking us for money.

68
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,896
When you came to the shop just now,

69
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,280
everyone could tell.

70
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,200
Actually,

71
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,600
I...

72
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,280
Xi Xi and I discussed it.

73
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,280
We can scrape together 6,000 yuan for you.

74
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,080
As for the rest, we neighbors

75
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,336
will help you think of something.

76
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,720
Don't feel pressured.

77
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:12,040
My best trait is my optimism.

78
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,920
Hello, Da Hei.

79
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:29,600
I... need a favor.

80
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,840
Well, here's the thing.

81
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,200
Something happened to my grandma.

82
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,960
She's in the hospital.

83
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:40,000
I'm a bit short on cash.

84
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,320
Can you lend me

85
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,160
5,000 yuan for now?

86
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,680
If not, 3,000,

87
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,880
or even 2,000 is fine.

88
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,720
Okay, okay. No problem.

89
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,400
Great.

90
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,880
Thanks a lot.

91
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,200
I really appreciate it.

92
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,040
Qing Ye,

93
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,240
can you tutor me in English?

94
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,640
I'll pay you.

95
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,160
Hello, Qing Ye.

96
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,137
Hello,

97
00:07:30,161 --> 00:07:31,881
about the English tutoring you mentioned

98
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,640
at 300 per lesson,

99
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,840
does the offer still stand?

100
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,040
Of course.

101
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,960
Okay, I'll do it.

102
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,160
But I have conditions.

103
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,760
Name them.

104
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,400
Pay a deposit up front.

105
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,360
Minimum booking of 10 lessons.

106
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,320
Book 10, get 1 free.

107
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,080
I decide the time and place.

108
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,960
No problem.

109
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,280
I'll take 20 lessons to start.

110
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,360
Okay.

111
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,120
(6,000 yuan sent. Please accept.)

112
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:25,200
Qing Ye, good morning.

113
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,600
- Shu Han.
- Get in.

114
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,056
Wait, I thought the
tutoring was in the evening.

115
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,720
Why are you here so early in the morning?

116
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,000
Shu Han said it's on her way.

117
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,640
She's giving us a ride to school today.

118
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,280
I have to pick you up anyway.

119
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,616
I'll drop them off at school,

120
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,800
then head to the county town.

121
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,760
Let's go.

122
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,520
I sent you the new contract.

123
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,496
It's been revised according
to your requirements.

124
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,400
When you have a moment,
take a good look at it.

125
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,840
Mr. Ye is being very sincere this time.

126
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,976
He wants to sign you on

127
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,216
as a full-time employee for three years.

128
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,336
Give it some serious thought.

129
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,040
I've read the contract. It looks fine.

130
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,416
Print it out and get the process started.

131
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,440
Okay.

132
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,360
Qing Ye, I have a contract too.

133
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,800
I thought about it last night.

134
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,960
I think our relationship

135
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,680
should be more formal.

136
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,120
What relationship?

137
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,120
A teacher-student relationship.

138
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,840
This contract is proof of that.

139
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,960
For these 20 lessons,

140
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,600
you can't skip a single one.

141
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,240
Not even the two free ones.

142
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,040
And no refunds allowed.

143
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,520
You're tutoring him?

144
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,240
Since when?

145
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,080
We agreed last night.

146
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,600
Starting today.

147
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,480
Xing Wu, look.

148
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,816
You and Shu Han

149
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,840
both work for my dad.

150
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:34,560
I'm a VVVIP at Xuandao,

151
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,400
and now Qing Ye is my teacher.

152
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,480
I think the Xuandao family and I

153
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,160
are really meant to be.

154
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,920
Get in the car.

155
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,600
Coming.

156
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,880
Ye Ying Jian, hurry up!

157
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:11,920
Coming! Give me a second.

158
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,720
Qing Ye, remember to sign the contract!

159
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,000
Qing Ye.

160
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,320
Could you not sign

161
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,240
that contract from Ye Ying Jian?

162
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,160
Then could you not sign

163
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,720
that contract from Shu Han?

164
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,016
Your job is to study hard here,

165
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:45,160
and leave this place after
the college entrance exam.

166
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,640
Tutoring is just a side thing.

167
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,120
It won't affect my studies.

168
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,280
I know you mean well,

169
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,200
- and want to help Grandma.
- Exactly.

170
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,880
You know

171
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,456
I can't just stand by and do nothing.

172
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:59,200
But earning a few thousand yuan
can't solve our family's problems.

173
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,040
In one more week,

174
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,480
I'll lose my student status.

175
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:10,560
Tell Zhu Feng to just cancel it.

176
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,040
You really don't plan to return to school?

177
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,280
No.

178
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:57,280
(Notice of Temporary
Closure for Corrective Action)

179
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,840
Liu Nian.

180
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,080
Ms. Fang.

181
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,240
This is an IOU.

182
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,760
Take it.

183
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,440
I'll pay back every cent I owe you.

184
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:21,000
During this time, find your friends,

185
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,040
and do some odd jobs.

186
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,216
When we're ready to reopen,

187
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,240
I'll let you know.

188
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,280
Ms. Fang, I haven't
worked these past few days.

189
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:29,040
Shouldn't you deduct that from my pay?

190
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,120
I won't deduct a single cent.

191
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,480
Just take it.

192
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,880
I have the money.

193
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,297
So, Ms. Fang,

194
00:12:37,321 --> 00:12:38,880
when can we reopen?

195
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,440
I believe

196
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,600
it will be very soon.

197
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,360
Who is it?

198
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,480
Coming!

199
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,000
Xiao Lian.

200
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,840
I... I'm here to see you.

201
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,560
Open the door and let me in.

202
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:13,617
Hey, Xiao Lian.

203
00:13:13,641 --> 00:13:15,656
Xiao Lian, I'm really here to apologize,

204
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:17,160
and patch things up with you.

205
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:24,200
Well... Xiao Lian, I'll head out then.

206
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,880
I'll leave the food I bought you

207
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,200
at the door.

208
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,400
Remember to eat it.

209
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,720
Xiao Lian.

210
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,120
Xiao Lian!

211
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,760
Xiao Lian. Xiao...

212
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,320
Xiao Lian.

213
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,520
This.

214
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:54,600
I spent money on all this.

215
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,480
Hand out the test papers to everyone.

216
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,600
Mr. Zhu.

217
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,200
Could you sign this for me?

218
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,840
- A leave request?
- Yes.

219
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,320
I'd like to be excused

220
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,016
from evening self-study
at school this week.

221
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,240
My grandma is in the hospital.

222
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,200
I need to be there with her.

223
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:37,440
But I promise I won't
fall behind in my studies.

224
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:38,800
Alright.

225
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,760
Thank you, Teacher.

226
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,600
Oh, Qing Ye.

227
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,360
About that thing I mentioned last time,

228
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:53,240
how did your talk with Xing Wu go?

229
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,640
Grandma needs looking after,

230
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,280
Xuandao has some issues to sort out,

231
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:00,000
and things at home are a mess.

232
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:03,896
I understand.

233
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:04,920
Alright, you can go.

234
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,600
(Name: Xing Wu)

235
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:38,760
Wu Zi.

236
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
Take a break.

237
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,640
I can sleep now.

238
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,760
Go to sleep.

239
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,760
Your student status has been canceled.

240
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,000
Don't you think it's a pity?

241
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,560
(Don't you think it's a pity?)

242
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:09,080
(It's not a pity at all.)

243
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:27,200
(Letter of Intent for Cooperation
with Electronics Street)

244
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,880
(Xing Wu)

245
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,080
Qing Ye.

246
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,320
Why are you leaving?

247
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,160
Aren't you staying for evening self-study?

248
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,440
I've taken leave.

249
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,680
Leave?

250
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,240
Did something happen?

251
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:11,760
Not really.

252
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,080
You suddenly want to tutor me.

253
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:17,600
Is it because my grades are good,

254
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,040
and you want to help me improve?

255
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:21,280
That way, we can get into
a good university together.

256
00:17:26,320 --> 00:17:27,440
You still look unhappy.

257
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,280
Are you short on money?

258
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,920
Is there anything that money can't solve?

259
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,400
I used to think like you.

260
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:44,576
But my recent experiences

261
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:45,600
have taught me

262
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,640
that some problems

263
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:50,080
cannot be solved with any amount of money.

264
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,056
Is there really anything

265
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,080
that money can't solve?

266
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,080
I used to be very confused.

267
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,296
Why couldn't he choose

268
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:06,080
his own life and destiny?

269
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,576
Then I put myself in his shoes,

270
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,600
and thought about it.

271
00:18:10,120 --> 00:18:11,120
If I were him,

272
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,120
would I have done any better?

273
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,000
Maybe I would've made the same choice.

274
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,120
"He"?

275
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,440
Who is "he"?

276
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,680
A family member.

277
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,680
Family?

278
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,040
I don't know how to comfort you,

279
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,640
or help your family.

280
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,160
But I do know,

281
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:35,680
if it were me,

282
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,400
I would stay by her side.

283
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:41,080
Even if I couldn't do anything.

284
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:47,720
Thank you for telling me that.

285
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:50,280
I'll get going then.

286
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:09,160
(Outpatient Building)

287
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,400
- Grandma.
- Xiao Ye.

288
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:36,920
You're here.

289
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:38,776
- How are you recovering?
- Did you get wet?

290
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:39,880
No, I'm fine.

291
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:42,080
How are you feeling?

292
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,440
Good.

293
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:46,080
Wu Zi has been here
taking care of me every day.

294
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,720
I'm recovering very well.

295
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,640
That's good.

296
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,440
I brought you some fish soup.

297
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,040
Drink plenty of it later.

298
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:55,176
It'll help you get some
calcium and recover faster.

299
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,200
Okay.

300
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,600
Okay, that's enough. Good.

301
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,400
Here.

302
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:02,920
- Okay.
- Here.

303
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,960
Piping hot fish soup.

304
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:12,920
- Here, have a taste.
- Okay.

305
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
How is it?

306
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:19,520
It's delicious.

307
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,680
Ian Fang made this soup, didn't she?

308
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,480
How did you know?

309
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:29,480
I've been eating her cooking for decades.

310
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,640
How could I not know?

311
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,600
Look.

312
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:35,600
When she makes fish soup,

313
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:38,000
there won't be a single bone in it.

314
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,400
Grandma.

315
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,640
Auntie asked me to tell you

316
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:49,160
that once she's settled
things with He Xiao Lian,

317
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,320
she'll come to see you.

318
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,200
Good.

319
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,880
Drink it while it's hot.

320
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:13,200
(Outpatient Building)

321
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,800
(Teachers' Office)

322
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:08,280
Come in.

323
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,440
I'm sorry.

324
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:11,280
Xing Wu's mom, what brings you here?

325
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:12,480
I

326
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,160
I'm here to bring you some soup.

327
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,176
Look at you, it's already noon.

328
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,840
Why are you still eating instant noodles?

329
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:19,840
You teach and shape your students.

330
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:21,440
Have some soup to nourish yourself.

331
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:23,000
It smells delicious.

332
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,120
Go ahead and drink it.

333
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,440
You're here for a reason, right?

334
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,720
Yes, I need your help with something.

335
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,840
I can probably guess what it is.

336
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:37,080
Well...

337
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,720
Xiao Lian has been avoiding me.

338
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:42,080
But I really need to see her.

339
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:44,096
So I was hoping you could help me...

340
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:45,120
No problem.

341
00:23:45,360 --> 00:23:46,456
After all, He Xiao Lian and I

342
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,856
were together for many years.

343
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,640
I know her temperament
and personality best.

344
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:52,080
How about this? I'll
go with you to see her.

345
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,720
You'll come with me?

346
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,960
- It's fine.
- Thank you, Mr. Zhu.

347
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,440
- Thank you.
- Don't mention it.

348
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,360
Just think of it as doing it for Xing Wu.

349
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,760
Xiao Lian, you're at home.

350
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,600
Xiao Lian.

351
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:14,336
- Xiao Lian. Xiao Lian!
- Xiao... Xiao Lian!

352
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,760
- Xiao Lian.
- Let go!

353
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:17,640
- Xiao Lian.
- We need to talk to you.

354
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:20,640
This is Li Ian Fang, the
mother of my student, Xing Wu.

355
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,000
Xiao Lian.

356
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:23,080
I'm sorry.

357
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:25,920
Well, I'm here to bring
you the money today.

358
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,880
It's so thin. This isn't 30,000, is it?

359
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:32,120
It's true, it's not 30,000.

360
00:24:33,120 --> 00:24:35,520
Your medical bill was 1,500.

361
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:36,960
As for the rest,

362
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:38,800
you can buy whatever you'd like with it.

363
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:40,520
We agreed on 30,000, so 30,000 it is.

364
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:41,800
Xiao Lian.

365
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:45,360
I had to scrape this money together.

366
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:48,000
Xuandao is closed while we sort things out,

367
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,200
and my mom is in the hospital too.

368
00:24:50,560 --> 00:24:51,720
That takes money too.

369
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:55,080
Our family is really struggling now.

370
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,200
We really can't come up with 30,000 yuan.

371
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,360
Look, it's not easy for anyone.

372
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:00,760
Besides,

373
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:02,520
your allergy looks almost healed.

374
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,000
Your tattooed eyebrows look great.

375
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:06,320
- You'll be fine in a few days.
- None of your business!

376
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,680
Li Ian Fang,

377
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:09,057
since you can't pay the 30,000,

378
00:25:09,081 --> 00:25:10,201
there's nothing more to say.

379
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:11,376
- Just leave.
- Xiao Lian.

380
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,440
I'm begging you.

381
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:14,320
Please, just take this money first.

382
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:16,016
Stop wasting your time!

383
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,600
- Go!
- I'll do anything you want!

384
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:18,800
I'll kneel to you.

385
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,040
I'll kneel down for you.

386
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:22,440
- You...
- I... Xiao Lian. I'm so sorry.

387
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,096
Li Ian Fang, come on. Get up, get up.

388
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:25,120
He Xiao Lian!

389
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,136
What are you doing?

390
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,160
Zhu Feng!

391
00:25:43,080 --> 00:25:44,800
That's enough already.

392
00:25:57,360 --> 00:25:58,360
Fine.

393
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:00,280
Let's leave it at that.

394
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:02,976
Come on, it's okay now.

395
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:04,000
Come.

396
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:07,000
- Is it settled then?
- It's settled.

397
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,720
Here, Xing Wu's mom.

398
00:26:24,800 --> 00:26:25,777
- Mr. Zhu.
- It's so hot today.

399
00:26:25,801 --> 00:26:27,401
- Here, have some milk tea.
- Thank you.

400
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:32,280
My students love this stuff.

401
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:34,200
It's good.

402
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,560
Mr. Zhu.

403
00:26:36,280 --> 00:26:37,280
I

404
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:38,640
I want to thank you.

405
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,440
You... You mean what happened just now?

406
00:26:42,280 --> 00:26:44,840
I could've just been the one to kneel.

407
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:47,160
But you came along and got scolded too.

408
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:49,600
You... Isn't it fine as long as it's settled?

409
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:50,880
I don't mind.

410
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:53,440
You don't know this. But
in front of He Xiao Lian,

411
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,640
I'm... used to it.

412
00:26:58,600 --> 00:26:59,600
Xiao Lian

413
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,000
she isn't a bad person.

414
00:27:01,080 --> 00:27:02,920
She's just too hot-tempered.

415
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:04,440
As for me, I'm too mild.

416
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:06,280
She always says to me, "Zhu Feng,"

417
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:07,337
"you're a grown man."

418
00:27:07,361 --> 00:27:08,761
"Why are you always so submissive?"

419
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,280
"A man should have some backbone."

420
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:11,360
"Don't you know that?"

421
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,320
How could I not know that?

422
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,480
I just feel that

423
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,176
a home isn't a place

424
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,320
where reason matters most.

425
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:20,080
Facing reality,

426
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:21,360
I can be flexible.

427
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:23,680
But my dreams have nowhere to go.

428
00:27:24,840 --> 00:27:26,680
Admitting my mistakes
isn't about compromise.

429
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:29,080
It's the wisdom of using
softness to overcome hardness.

430
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,217
It's just that...

431
00:27:30,241 --> 00:27:31,520
He Xiao Lian is too hard.

432
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:33,000
I've never managed to overcome her.

433
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,416
Mr. Zhu,

434
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,417
whatever comes out of your mouth

435
00:27:35,441 --> 00:27:37,760
always sounds very reasonable.

436
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,880
Well, I am a teacher, after all.

437
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,040
Actually, Xing Wu's mom,

438
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,480
I quite admire you.

439
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:45,960
Admire me?

440
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,856
I've made such a mess of my life.

441
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,880
What is there to admire?

442
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,480
Have you heard of trigonometric functions?

443
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:55,840
What?

444
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,576
Trigonometric functions.

445
00:27:58,600 --> 00:27:59,896
Their periodic fluctuations

446
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,080
follow a predictable pattern.

447
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:03,600
The highs and lows alternate.

448
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,600
It's a bit like our lives.

449
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,696
Look, you might be

450
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,240
at a low point in your life right now.

451
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,960
But I believe

452
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,200
that as long as you

453
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,840
live your life positively,

454
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,856
sooner or later, you'll trace out

455
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,880
a perfect curve.

456
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,280
One that shows an upward trend.

457
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,360
Mr. Zhu, I understand.

458
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:23,160
You mean to say my luck is about to change?

459
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,000
Something like that.

460
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,120
From your lips to God's ears!

461
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:28,560
Well...

462
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:31,176
May the Sea Goddess bless me.

463
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:32,560
Bless me, Li Ian Fang.

464
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:34,120
Let my luck change soon!

465
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:37,400
Mr. Zhu, when you come to Xuandao,

466
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,680
I'll give you a free haircut.

467
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:41,496
That wouldn't be right. Things
aren't easy for you either.

468
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:43,080
If you really want to thank me,

469
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:44,937
then do this.

470
00:28:44,961 --> 00:28:46,441
Have Xing Wu come thank me at school.

471
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:50,920
Actually, the way Wu Zi is now...

472
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:53,000
It's all my fault as his mother.

473
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,400
Don't say that.

474
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:56,400
Xing Wu is a good kid.

475
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,400
I just think it's a shame
for him to quit school.

476
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,696
The children's future shouldn't be ruined

477
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:03,240
by the difficulties we adults face.

478
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:04,920
Don't you agree?

479
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,720
Yes.

480
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,360
Well, since I'm helping you out,

481
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,840
how about I give you a ride back?

482
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,417
Sure.

483
00:29:17,441 --> 00:29:18,520
- Watch your step.
- Okay.

484
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,640
Xing Wu's mom,

485
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:24,720
this next song is dedicated to you!

486
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,480
Great!

487
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:00,920
I'm home.

488
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:01,960
You're back.

489
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:04,880
I heard from Zhu Feng

490
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:06,920
that you settled the compensation issue.

491
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:09,840
He told you?

492
00:30:12,120 --> 00:30:14,080
Why would he tell you

493
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,456
about all my embarrassing secrets?

494
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,480
Embarrassing secrets?

495
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,040
What did he tell you?

496
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,600
He said

497
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:25,360
you're a steel rose.

498
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,600
"Turning the tide when all is lost..."

499
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,800
"And holding it all together
when it's falling apart."

500
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,840
I only understood the first part.

501
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,457
Well,

502
00:30:36,481 --> 00:30:37,920
the rest is true as well.

503
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,680
By the way, is Grandma
getting discharged

504
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:42,840
this weekend?

505
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:45,136
The doctor said she's recovering well.

506
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,960
She can come home to
recuperate this weekend.

507
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:47,976
That's great.

508
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,977
I've been busy these past few days

509
00:30:49,001 --> 00:30:50,136
sorting out the licensing paperwork.

510
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,960
I'll get her room ready in a bit.

511
00:30:52,080 --> 00:30:53,080
I'll do it.

512
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:55,416
Also, I ordered

513
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,440
a new roll-up banner.

514
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,880
Aren't we reopening soon?

515
00:30:57,920 --> 00:31:00,000
When you're free, help me go pick it up.

516
00:31:00,520 --> 00:31:01,520
Sure.

517
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:09,400
(Zhazhating)

518
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,000
They're here.

519
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,120
They're here.

520
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:21,360
She's back, she's back.

521
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:22,520
Wu Zi.

522
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:24,600
Mom.

523
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:25,720
Careful, careful.

524
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,200
Careful, Mom. Don't rush.

525
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:28,720
I'm back.

526
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,120
- Slowly.
- Slowly.

527
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,400
- Thank you, sir.
- Careful.

528
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,840
Xiao Ye.

529
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,376
- Okay, thank you.
- We're home.

530
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,016
- Mom, Mom.
- Ian Fang.

531
00:31:37,040 --> 00:31:38,280
Mom, how are you feeling?

532
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:40,040
- Are you okay?
- Good.

533
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:41,577
Let me tell you,

534
00:31:41,601 --> 00:31:43,240
everything is sorted out now.

535
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,240
The business license is ready too.

536
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,800
Look, we even put up

537
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:48,360
a grand reopening sign.

538
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:50,400
That's wonderful.

539
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:52,616
You won't make that mistake again, right?

540
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,200
I won't, I won't. Never again.

541
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,600
Then, let's take a photo.

542
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,176
- Sure, to celebrate the occasion.
- Let's do it.

543
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,200
- Okay.
- Grandma.

544
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:02,016
- Come on.
- Everyone, get ready.

545
00:32:02,040 --> 00:32:03,600
I'll count down from three!

546
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:04,657
- Okay.
- Okay.

547
00:32:04,681 --> 00:32:06,800
Three, two, one.

548
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,656
Cheese!

549
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,680
One more.

550
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:12,520
Three, two, one.

551
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,280
Cheese!

552
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,440
Help me check. Is it straight?

553
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,400
- It's crooked.
- No, it's crooked.

554
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,296
- No. To the right.
- How about now? Is it straight?

555
00:32:21,320 --> 00:32:23,360
- To the right a little.
- It's still crooked, son.

556
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:24,600
Is it straight?

557
00:32:24,760 --> 00:32:25,896
It's just right now.

558
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:26,896
- That's it.
- Okay.

559
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:27,896
It's good?

560
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:28,920
I'll listen to Grandma.

561
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:34,360
Looking at this photo
really warms my heart.

562
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,160
Our Xuandao will surely
get better and better.

563
00:32:37,360 --> 00:32:39,240
Harmony in the family brings prosperity.

564
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:41,200
Exactly. Auntie,

565
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:43,280
with your optimistic attitude,

566
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:45,440
you'll succeed in anything.

567
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,736
Ms. Fang, I believe

568
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:48,880
you'll lead Xuandao

569
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,016
to grow bigger and stronger.

570
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,216
- Good.
- Bigger and stronger!

571
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:52,520
Yes, bigger and stronger!

572
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,616
- Bigger and stronger!
- Bigger and stronger!

573
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:54,640
Good, good.

574
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:58,960
(Xuandao Show Hair Salon)

575
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,680
Here.

576
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:09,160
The weather changed so fast.

577
00:33:09,320 --> 00:33:10,680
It was clear and sunny just now.

578
00:33:11,080 --> 00:33:12,080
Suddenly, it's raining.

579
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:13,880
That's life, I guess.

580
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:15,600
One second,

581
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,040
it's clear and sunny.

582
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,280
The next, it's a storm.

583
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,640
So, Boss Xing,

584
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:23,960
when are you planning to
start your job in the county?

585
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:26,520
I haven't decided yet.

586
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,720
Did you delay it because
of Grandma's situation?

587
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,200
No.

588
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,040
What?

589
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:39,080
Do you want to persuade
me to go back to school again?

590
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:44,800
If taking that job in the county

591
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,896
is the best choice you can make

592
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,920
at this moment,

593
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:49,960
I won't oppose it anymore.

594
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,280
No more pushing me to study?

595
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,600
No more.

596
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:57,760
Why?

597
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:00,480
Because I believe in you.

598
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:02,520
No matter which path you take,

599
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,880
even if it's stormy along the way,

600
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:07,720
you will reach your own Rome.

601
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:09,600
And I promise,

602
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:11,960
no matter what you decide,

603
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:14,400
I will firmly support you.

604
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:17,920
I got it.

605
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:55,760
How could she be like this?

606
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,440
- This is mind-blowing.
- Look.

607
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,840
I thought her family was poor.

608
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:02,160
Turns out she's a rich kid.

609
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:03,896
Yet she had the nerve to
take the living allowance.

610
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,240
Her family has a criminal record.

611
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,896
Then she can't become
a civil servant, right?

612
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,680
Her dad's money is suspicious.

613
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,856
How could she be any good herself?

614
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,880
Look, it's her.

615
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:12,200
It's her.

616
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,880
Qing Ye.

617
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:16,080
Qing Ye.

618
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,640
This is bad. Something happened.

619
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,816
- What's wrong?
- Did you see the post

620
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:19,840
on the campus forum?

621
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,200
What post?

622
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:29,016
(She thought she could hide here
and that no one would find out...)

623
00:35:29,040 --> 00:35:30,640
(about the dirty secrets in her family.)

624
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:34,856
(Such a poser. Always
stealing the spotlight.)

625
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,800
(Shouldn't the school
take this more seriously?)

626
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:43,216
Stop it. The more you comb it,

627
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:44,800
the more it looks like a dog chewed it.

628
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,600
It actually was chewed by a dog.

629
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:50,640
Where did you get it cut? I
really need to avoid that place.

630
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,520
Want some? My family dried them.

631
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,600
Aren't you afraid of me?

632
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,840
No.

633
00:36:19,040 --> 00:36:20,816
Those people just believe
whatever rumors they hear.

634
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,840
Not me.

635
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,280
Shi Min.

636
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,800
Qing Ye, come here!

637
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,160
I saved you a seat. Hurry.

638
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,120
Chicken leg.

639
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,440
- What are you doing?
- Are you blind?

640
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,240
Why did you bump into her on purpose?

641
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,800
I'm sorry.

642
00:36:56,160 --> 00:36:57,160
Are you okay?

643
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,120
I'm sorry.

644
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:04,336
I didn't do it on purpose either.

645
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,976
- It was an accident.
- Are you crazy?

646
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,000
You did that on purpose.

647
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,360
Well, we didn't do it on purpose.

648
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:11,080
Qing Ye, you're the one who
dirtied Li Wen Hui's clothes!

649
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:12,400
Everyone saw it clearly!

650
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:13,600
Don't you all agree?

651
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,560
- Yes!
- Yes, my foot!

652
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:17,640
Forget it, Fang Lei.
She's protected by thugs.

653
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:19,016
We can't afford to mess with her.

654
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:20,456
If you've got a problem, come at me.

655
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,040
There's no need to drag others into it!

656
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,336
Then what about you bullying...

657
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,640
Fang Lei and the others?

658
00:37:24,720 --> 00:37:26,200
What do you have to say for yourself?

659
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:28,040
Me? Bullying them?

660
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:31,000
Zhu... Zhu... Zhu.

661
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:32,680
- Mr. Zhu!
- What's wrong?

662
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,816
Qing Ye got into a fight

663
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,840
in the cafeteria.

664
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,640
You chopped off both their hair.

665
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:40,720
You even threatened
them not to tell anyone.

666
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,040
Isn't that bullying?

667
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:45,320
Fang Lei, am I telling the truth?

668
00:37:46,680 --> 00:37:48,240
- I...
- Of course it is!

669
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,440
Look at Fang Lei's hair.
It's completely ruined.

670
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,136
You guys were the ones who started it.

671
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:54,240
I was being bullied. Am I
not allowed to fight back?

672
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:56,456
You scratched her hand, didn't you?

673
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,680
Isn't that bullying?

674
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,960
It was self-defense. Believe it or not.

675
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:01,680
Stop right there!

676
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:04,560
Fang Lei and Li Wen
Hui just want an apology.

677
00:38:04,600 --> 00:38:05,600
Is that too much to ask?

678
00:38:06,080 --> 00:38:07,496
Just because you're from the big city,

679
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:08,856
you think you can twist the truth.

680
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,240
We just want an apology.

681
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:13,576
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

682
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:15,280
- Shut up!
- You'd better apologize!

683
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,360
Shut up!

684
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,377
Shut your mouth!

685
00:38:17,401 --> 00:38:20,480
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

686
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,600
Shut your mouth!

687
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:23,840
- Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!
- Shut up!

688
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:26,976
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

689
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:27,977
Shut up!

690
00:38:28,001 --> 00:38:29,416
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

691
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,417
- Come with me.
- Apologize!

692
00:38:30,441 --> 00:38:35,040
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

693
00:38:59,600 --> 00:39:00,600
Qing Ye, what's going on?

694
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:01,960
Xing Wu! Where are you going?

695
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,160
You're such a bully!

696
00:39:25,760 --> 00:39:27,320
Bully!

697
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,377
The teacher is here!

698
00:39:28,401 --> 00:39:29,920
How can you be such a bully?

699
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,520
You're bullying her!

700
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,240
What are you all doing?

701
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:44,560
This is the cafeteria. It's a place to eat.

702
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,120
Let me remind you all.

703
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,816
Every one of you here

704
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:51,960
will only be a high school
student once in your life.

705
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:56,320
Don't do anything you'll
look back on and regret

706
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,040
years after graduation.

707
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,920
I'll hold onto this.

708
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:28,320
You must be hungry.

709
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,320
Try some.

710
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,760
What is this?

711
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:33,440
Agar jelly.

712
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:34,960
It's a local specialty.

713
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,840
Go ahead and eat. It's not poisoned.

714
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:50,480
It's savory.

715
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,800
It's good, right?

716
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,456
Didn't you go with Shu Han

717
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:01,480
to see Mr. Ye?

718
00:42:02,200 --> 00:42:03,200
Why are you here?

719
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:05,360
What a coincidence, right?

720
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,880
I was just passing by.

721
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:16,080
Mr. Wu, emergency!

722
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:17,280
Qing Ye is in trouble.

723
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,856
Qing Ye, you're the one

724
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:19,856
who dirtied Li Wen Hui's clothes!

725
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:20,880
I have to go.

726
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:22,040
Something urgent came up.

727
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:24,240
What about Mr. Ye?

728
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,840
You know how rare this opportunity is.

729
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:27,240
Apologize to him for me.

730
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,576
I'll make it up to him next time.

731
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:29,600
Xing Wu!

732
00:42:32,720 --> 00:42:33,720
I originally thought

733
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:37,000
that once I got to Zhazhating,

734
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,480
everything would come to an end.

735
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,120
I thought I could start over.

736
00:42:48,160 --> 00:42:49,160
This is a small town.

737
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:51,240
Even the smallest thing

738
00:42:51,600 --> 00:42:53,240
will spread like wildfire.

739
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,320
Everyone's life is boring,

740
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:57,160
so they like to be spectators.

741
00:42:57,600 --> 00:42:58,577
They love a good story.

742
00:42:58,601 --> 00:42:59,840
So they'll add their own spin,

743
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:01,017
make things up,

744
00:43:01,041 --> 00:43:02,280
and pass off fiction as fact.

745
00:43:03,040 --> 00:43:04,600
The more bizarre, the better.

746
00:43:05,040 --> 00:43:06,040
Exactly.

747
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,720
They don't care about the truth.

748
00:43:08,680 --> 00:43:10,016
But they also have short memories.

749
00:43:10,040 --> 00:43:11,600
In a few days, when new gossip arrives,

750
00:43:11,880 --> 00:43:13,680
the old stories are completely forgotten.

751
00:43:15,080 --> 00:43:16,080
Don't take it to heart.

752
00:43:17,040 --> 00:43:18,280
The rumor-mongers might forget,

753
00:43:18,600 --> 00:43:19,960
but what about the victims?

754
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:22,400
What about the pain they've suffered?

755
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:31,080
What are you doing?

756
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:32,920
Close your eyes.

757
00:43:33,240 --> 00:43:34,240
Close your eyes.

758
00:43:43,680 --> 00:43:44,680
Take a deep breath.
